{"tid":1179304,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[萊利非常識] 稀土其實唔太稀有！","createTime":"2019-05-31T04:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T04:48:12.000Z","uid":136312,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1127a7d6099e634456d11e452705cbeaeb738c00","tid":1179304,"uid":136312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/05/31/2Jlv5P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F05%2F31%2F2Jlv5P.png&h=627db0b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n萊利非常識 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/roycommonsense \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Froycommonsense%20&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=d39bcb0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/roycommonsense </a><br />\n<br />\n「稀土」中的「土」字實際上指的是氧化物。這些元素被發現時人們以為它們在地球上分布非常稀少。實際上它們在地殼內的含量並不算太低，最高的鈰是地殼中第25豐富的元素，比鉛還要高，而「稀土金屬」中穩定元素里豐度最低的鎦在地殼中的含量比金甚至還要高出200倍。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711fbb1929ee5918aa4aa5b96ff6453ed8c08455","tid":1179304,"uid":164331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1127a7d6099e634456d11e452705cbeaeb738c00","tid":1179304,"uid":136312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/05/31/2Jlv5P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F05%2F31%2F2Jlv5P.png&h=627db0b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n萊利非常識 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/roycommonsense \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Froycommonsense%20&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=d39bcb0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/roycommonsense </a><